  "title": "Sales Executive (Construction) #76395",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Building & Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Executive (Construction)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Tampines</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Monday - Friday, 8.30am - 5.30pm, Saturday 8.30am - 12.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic + AWS + Transport Allowance (if have own vehicle)</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Draft and follow up on sales quotations and proposals tailored to client needs.</li><li>Handle all sales documentation and perform related administrative tasks.</li><li>Coordinate with clients, vendors, and suppliers for seamless project execution.</li><li>Develop new business connections, identify prospects, and promote the company’s offerings.</li><li>Cultivate and sustain relationships with both existing clients and potential customers.</li><li>Negotiate deals, close sales, and collect feedback to improve services.</li><li>Create and deliver presentations on company’s products and services.</li><li>Conduct market research to identify sales opportunities and potential new clients.</li><li>Meet or exceed sales goals and contribute to overall business objectives.</li><li>Gather and analyze data to generate sales reports.</li><li>Other tasks as directed by Manager.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in Construction, Mechanical Engineering, Sales, Marketing, or a related field is preferred.</li><li>At least 1 year of sales experience desired.</li><li>Preference for candidates with a Class 3 Driving License and their own vehicle, although this is not mandatory.</li><li>Individuals without experience are encouraged to apply, training is provided.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76395 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
